title: The Socially Umpired Animals
description:
6529 Meme Cards. 2023 June #118. Speaking the words of a forgotten playbook,   
Seize the memes of production, captivatingly.   
Cages of thought lock the mind in a classroom;   
Covering the walls with the blanket of language.   
Happiness and sorrows paint stories on canvases,   
Seeking meaning from a lexicon of symbols.   
Yearning to break out and break free,   
The animals are on a quest for the light.   
Scurrying to end a never-ending wait,   
Shouting from behind bars in deep despair.   
Racing beyond their socially umpired course,   
They battle onwards with a roar of hope.   
  
Meme: 1  
Season: 3  
Card: 8

openSea.description:
The Memes Collection is focused on the fight for the open metaverse (decentralization, community, self-sovereignty) and spreading this message to many people, many wallets.

It is a collection that is meant to be open and accessible. Edition sizes will generally be large and inexpensive, to spread the word and to avoid gas wars.

We will try to have a good time along the way, make some fun art, do great collabs and just generally have a good time.

For more information visit https://6529.io/collections/the-memes/
